 201.0582, 200.7807, 199.6713, 199.8871, 199.5326, 198.7446, 199.0648, 199.7825, 199.8156, 201.9627, 203.4722, 202.3552, 201.649, 201.8809, 200.9118, 199.8909, 198.7663, 197.7054, 197.9075, 197.1849, 197.5144, 198.446, 198.0504, 197.4899, 198.1497, 198.1913, 198.6836, 198.6532, 198.575, 198.6142, 198.2872, 197.9242, 198.4171, 198.8693, 199.4454, 199.918, 199.8334, 199.5748, 198.2998, 198.3724, 197.7835, 198.7696, 197.8326, 198.0167, 198.2882, 197.7254, 197.6599, 197.5764, 198.2317, 198.7355, 198.77, 197.1894, 198.2721, 198.2169, 198.5325, 199.4798, 198.8016, 196.7273, 196.4821, 195.03, 193.8324, 194.4652, 194.8411, 195.3114, 194.1415, 194.3876, 194.7666, 195.765, 196.8558, 197.3311, 197.2698, 198.6809, 197.6441, 198.4635, 199.1869, 200.6719, 200.2338, 199.7989, 199.0917, 199.5132, 200.2198, 201.3964, 201.5251, 200.9188, 202.1402, 202.7651, 203.2961, 203.29, 202.7242, 202.6084, 202.4626, 202.2854, 202.1227, 202.3158, 202.3815, 201.7968, 201.2953, 201.518, 200.9577, 200.8669, 201.0099, 200.3286, 200.561, 201.3285, 200.4344, 201.412, 201.2104, 201.6047, 201.2751, 200.173, 201.273, 200.972, 201.2093, 202.0104, 202.4535, 202.113, 203.0873, 203.9163, 203.7865, 203.0502, 203.7727, 205.1563, 205.3463, 204.7351, 204.9583, 204.1749, 204.1036, 205.7907, 205.7385, 205.3036, 204.7649, 204.665, 203.0377, 206.1394, 205.1072, 205.1774, 205.4748, 207.0085, 207.1827, 205.8184, 206.0802, 208.0625, 207.2115, 206.5071, 207.0333, 206.3251, 207.7808, 208.4235, 207.3468, 206.905, 207.4888, 206.1526, 206.1756, 209.4811, 207.7679, 209.7079, 210.6137, 209.5348, 211.1905, 211.0214, 210.5663, 211.2137, 207.4611, 207.6916, 204.4723, 206.6279, 203.5986, 201.6499, 201.49], "summary_html": "<h1>铅基本面量化因子挖掘 -- 截面化推广</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原文研究了铅市场中再生铅与原生铅的价差机制：当铅价高企时，再生铅利润丰厚，供应弹性大，贴水出货挤占原生铅需求，压制价格；反之铅价低位时再生铅利润萎缩，供应收紧，原生铅需求增加，构成价格下沿支撑。这一\"利润驱动供应弹性→价差锚定震荡区间\"的逻辑，本质上是基本面均值回归的一个特例。</p>\n<p>由于原文使用的再生铅-原生铅价差数据（SMM外部数据）不可得，我们将核心逻辑拆解为三个可截面化推广的基本面因子： 1. <strong>基差因子（basis）</strong>: 高基差（backwardation）=库存紧张=做多，低基差（contango）=供应充裕=做空 2. <strong>库存变化率因子（inventory_cr）</strong>: 库存累积=需求弱=做空，库存消耗=需求强=做多 3. <strong>利润因子（profit_chg）</strong>: 高利润=供应扩张压力=做空，低利润=供应收缩=做多</p>\n<p>最终最优方案为基差+库存两因子等权组合的截面排名策略，利润因子因信号质量弱（Sharpe &lt; 0.3）被从组合中降权。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.09</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-6.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.43</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.12</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.75 / 1.18</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.41</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.01</span></td><td>1.42</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.51</span></td><td>0.81</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.33</span></td><td>1.83</td><td>0.81</td><td>1.55</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.13</span></td><td>1.79</td><td>1.03</td><td>0.03</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.68</span></td><td>0.32</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 60 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 60 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>61</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>40.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<h3>基差因子</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_norm}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{basis}_{i,t}}{\\text{close}_{i,t}}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_ma}_{i,t}^{W} = \\frac{1}{W}\\sum_{k=0}^{W-1} \\text{basis\\_norm}_{i,t-k}</div>\n<h3>库存变化率因子</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv\\_cr}_{i,t}^{M} = \\frac{\\text{Inv}_{i,t}}{\\frac{1}{M}\\sum_{k=0}^{M-1}\\text{Inv}_{i,t-k}} - 1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Inv}</span> 优先使用 <code>inventory_21</code>，缺失时回退至 <code>receipt</code>，并做 forward-fill。</p>\n<h3>组合信号</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}_{i,t} = \\text{rank}^{CS}(\\text{basis\\_ma}_{i,t}) + (1 - \\text{rank}^{CS}(\\text{inv\\_cr}_{i,t}))</div>\n<p>对 combo 再做截面排名，通过 <code>rank_to_continuous</code> 转为 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, +1]</span> 连续仓位信号。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>单因子basis最强(1.18)，profit极弱(0.08)，turnover=0.58</td><td>实现profit/inv/basis三因子+combo，无hold约束</td><td>Sharpe 1.18，但basis独大</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>加入rebalance_hold降低换手；basis+inv组合优于三因子</td><td>增加H5/H10持仓约束，2因子combo替代3因子</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>: Sharpe 1.18→1.45，bi_basis_ma20_60_H10_raw最优</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>H10已不错，尝试更长持仓H15/H20；加inv_cr80窗口</td><td>扩展H15/H20+inv80网格，加CS归一化</td><td>Sharpe 1.45→1.47（CS归一化小幅提升）</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键发现</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>基差是最强因子，利润因子在截面维度几乎无效（可能是因为利润数据更新频率低）</li>\n<li>库存变化率与基差互补，2因子组合稳定优于单因子</li>\n<li>rebalance_hold(H10-H15) 显著降低换手成本，提升净Sharpe</li>\n<li>截面标准化(CS)对连续信号有小幅提升</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（58个商品期货），需 basis/inventory 非空</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 15天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库中 xinye 库存因子相关性 0.54（corr &gt; 0.5），但本策略 Sharpe(1.47) &gt; xinye(1.12)\n<p>- 2024-2025 年度 Sharpe 接近零，近期信号有效性减弱 - 利润因子截面信号弱，可能是数据质量问题（利润数据更新不及时） - 原文针对铅单品种（短期样本 Sharpe 3.22），全品种推广后 Sharpe 下降属预期</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>INV_M</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>inventory change-rate lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>BASIS_W</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>basis_norm MA window</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>rebalance hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>SCALE</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>rank_to_continuous scale</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.16s</li>\n</ul>"}